snippet.title: A Steamboat Willie Official Gameplay Teaser 2 | 2024
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam right now -  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2426070/Steamboat_Willie/

Discord - https://discord.gg/DSynEh4S4f

The game is set to release between late january and early march 2024. If there are wishes to get a closed alpha key you can join the Discord.

All images and music used in this video is public domain. 
This game is NOT made by or with Disney and does in noway, shape, or form try to missinform potential buyers/consumers.
